{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "22bd4bfe-dae7-4358-8b28-751fac1850e9",
    "name": "Interact with Painting",
    "sceneId": "e01d8134-66fb-415c-ada1-c9446206097f",
    "propId": "55470a04-5b3f-4cff-a48b-af3e3127c15b",
    "actorId": null,
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.interact",
        "name": "Interact"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "1fc406dc-18f9-452f-a4bb-31cac8d4ea28",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "d4ed1f27-e016-46b1-a8bc-1bde8f17fe27",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "6f48a04e-2e2e-419b-8221-b99f816feb9a",
                            "text": "Examine the Painting",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showCloseUp",
                                    "imageName": "CU_DonalAndShamus.png"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ec06c23e-8307-4bde-b3c2-1cc747bc6b20",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "The plaque says, \"Donal and Shamus O'Conner with the Raven of Sardonia.\"",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "781fff5f-abe4-4417-a52c-93a69b076eac",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "My father and his brother holding the Raven statue - my father must really have been the king of thieves. I could have been a prince of thieves.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "34ca522b-02df-4ba2-8ad4-75eeb5a44b7b",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "If only he hadn't died.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ed45b6d9-ae69-4b37-b5c6-bea63d2cef4a",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I look a lot like my father. Mama always told me that, but now I can see for myself.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7b3d003a-137b-45ad-8550-72947e4a540a",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I wish I could talk to him right now. I have so many questions to ask. How did he die? Was he really murdered? What happened to the Raven statue? ",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4eee1cf0-5b81-4b9c-a6be-87e54d9aa29a",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I've missed my father all my life and yet, I had no idea who or what he really was.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.hideCloseUp",
                                    "waitForSeconds": 1
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "7",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "b295c23a-7c19-4b89-bd50-7e8d7203ddb0",
                            "text": "Look Behind the Painting",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "93146e6c-cc38-4d7d-9a16-086a82398ad4",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "How cool would it be to find a secret door behind the painting that led to my father's secret chamber? Maybe he'd still be there waiting for me where he's been in hiding all this time.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "cba46f96-6aa0-4262-83e2-b7df29c2d026",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I could yell at him for leaving us all these years. For leaving us with so many questions...",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "40afbced-df59-4c34-bfa3-99695c77ec86",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "But no... there's only solid wall behind the painting.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.branch",
                                    "sections": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": {
                                                "type": "expressions.and",
                                                "left": {
                                                    "type": "expressions.skillCheck",
                                                    "skill": "Perception",
                                                    "target": "65"
                                                },
                                                "right": {
                                                    "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                                    "scope": "target",
                                                    "scopeId": null,
                                                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                                                    "tags": "gotletter",
                                                    "has": false
                                                }
                                            },
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "e13563c4-e148-43d2-9acc-c3579582bb76",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "Wait... there's something stuck on the back of the painting.",
                                                    "emotion": "4",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "d0905e97-6082-414b-bd72-b014b118bec4",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "It's a folded note tucked away in the frame.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                                    "id": "a6f85fe9-eb6b-4011-9606-3a3091657fc1",
                                                    "scriptId": "22bd4bfe-dae7-4358-8b28-751fac1850e9",
                                                    "entryPointId": "ac04a661-16fd-47c1-a8c2-164e7d3fe262",
                                                    "currentScope": "Current",
                                                    "currentSceneId": null,
                                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                                    "currentPropId": null
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "ef7e7f6a-0389-4eea-b9c8-e9d1caedac40",
                            "text": "Look at the Back of the Painting",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.branch",
                                    "sections": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": {
                                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                                "scope": "target",
                                                "scopeId": null,
                                                "scopeFilterId": null,
                                                "tags": "gotLetter",
                                                "has": false
                                            },
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                                    "id": "f8b90a94-0d2f-4fb2-854b-c5fbf2f8fb38",
                                                    "scriptId": "22bd4bfe-dae7-4358-8b28-751fac1850e9",
                                                    "entryPointId": "ac04a661-16fd-47c1-a8c2-164e7d3fe262",
                                                    "currentScope": "Current",
                                                    "currentSceneId": null,
                                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                                    "currentPropId": null
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "6b482829-c02f-4298-a6fc-8375a05415e7",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "There's nothing else on the back of the painting but memories and dust.",
                                                    "emotion": "2",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": {
                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                "scope": "actor",
                                "scopeId": "feffd7f3-810e-4625-9d22-dafc701d17e0",
                                "scopeFilterId": null,
                                "tags": "LetterHint",
                                "has": true
                            },
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "769cfbe9-df54-469e-8764-82816f6c0fc2",
                            "text": "Steal the Painting",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9f65ebe7-474e-4e48-847e-b6f2d77d7ec8",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "No way I would steal that painting. I don't really want to see my father's smiling face staring proud and smug at me like that. It makes me feel angry and sad at the same time.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "e08634ff-2b7f-4f26-8016-b3794c46ca6c",
                            "text": "Sense Magic on the Painting",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.hideCloseUp",
                                    "waitForSeconds": 1
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                    "id": "4cba743d-058a-4e36-80d9-dc354bd3e72a",
                                    "scriptId": "533e1ce1-13d3-439f-8544-dbdf808d30c4",
                                    "entryPointId": "1fc406dc-18f9-452f-a4bb-31cac8d4ea28",
                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                    "currentSceneId": "5f4c53b2-540d-4627-af71-7ede35c6d84b",
                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                    "currentPropId": null
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": {
                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                "scope": "actor",
                                "scopeId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                "scopeFilterId": null,
                                "tags": "SenseMagic",
                                "has": true
                            },
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": true,
                    "Unique": false
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "ac04a661-16fd-47c1-a8c2-164e7d3fe262",
            "name": "GetLetter",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeTags",
                    "id": "10765ac4-ac80-4fe1-9e45-f3af0d1952ab",
                    "scope": "target",
                    "scopeId": null,
                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                    "tagsToAdd": "gotLetter",
                    "tagsToRemove": null
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showCloseUp",
                    "imageName": "letterFromDonal.png"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "948e610e-f7ea-4cca-bd37-13629155601b",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Wha... it's a letter addressed to me... from my father!",
                    "emotion": "4",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "038dafc6-094b-4d27-898e-dff9314fd165",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "It says:\n<i>Shawn, my dearest son,\nThere's so much I need to tell you when you grow up, but there's none of us can see the future. It's dangerous times and I may not be here when you are a man. I'll tell you plain - you gotta do what needs be done, no matter what.</i>",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "898bda87-17ab-49aa-90b8-0dfd16338077",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "<i>In Eire, me brother Shamus and I, we fought to free our homeland from the tyranny of Albion. It had to be done. That made us outlaws in the eyes of the Queen's men. We had no choice but to flee Eire with the greatest of treasures - your mother, Nora.</i>",
                    "emotion": "4",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "0930b12f-cccf-463d-947c-55e2f34003cc",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "<i>Alas, in Sardonia, there was naught for us but to be beggars or thieves. You do what you must, so I tried to be the best of thieves. 'Twas cruel and vicious work. The king of thieves, the Raven, took the best of every theft. He let his followers starve. He was just another tyrant who needed to be taken down.</i>",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c629712c-501d-4492-8c88-685d24cd266e",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "<i>And take him down, I did. I became the Raven of Sardonia. I was as fair to my people as could be. We thieves grew strong and powerful. 'Twas said that I ruled Sardonia more than the prince.</i>",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "b8b7fe49-81c0-4b92-9568-d04d4a25deac",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "<i>Nora, though, she hated what I did. Thieves is thieves, she said, there's no good to come of them. I didn't listen. I was blinded by power and could not see the harm I was doing to this land.</i>",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "fa204df2-1f1c-44b8-ae3a-69c905e0ee2c",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "<i>Then a former Chief Thief from another land came to me and told me to open my eyes. As the thieves grew stronger, the land suffered. Traders stayed away. Children were starving. People lived in fear. I had become a tyrant, too.</i>",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "9c9816af-d38e-4995-980f-d5f5b778347e",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "<i>You gotta do what needs be done. I now will end this kingdom of thieves. There will be no Raven to rule in Sardonia from here on. I will make things right.</i>",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "283d418b-d1d3-4aa1-b890-1929cf046d68",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "<i>Whatever happens from this point on, I hope you're well and happy. Take care of your mother for me. I know that your Uncle Shamus will be watching over you. I love you, Shawn.\nYour father, Donal</i>",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.wait",
                    "waitForSeconds": "1"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.hideCloseUp",
                    "waitForSeconds": 1
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "b806270b-9faa-44e3-9e7b-45210d80db39",
                    "name": "Letter from My Father",
                    "notify": true,
                    "description": "So my father was a freedom fighter, a thief, and King of the Thieves. Then he tried to make sure no one would ever be King of Thieves again. Guess he succeeded at that.\n\nI don't know how he died. I don't really know what to think about him right now. Guess he really did love me. \n\nI just feel sad and miss him more than ever. "
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "91b5f60b-404b-40bc-ac54-b13bfac80be4",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I guess my father really did love me. I wish I had gotten to know him better.",
                    "emotion": "2",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}